  "detailed_description": "Save the galaxy and its taste in music, in this self-inflicted bullet hell - Pew! Pew! Pew!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/51cfa7da25032cd97099cfdb809ad16e.poster.avif?t=1726150836\" width=584 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/51cfa7da25032cd97099cfdb809ad16e.webm?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/51cfa7da25032cd97099cfdb809ad16e.mp4?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join the Laser Disco Defenders on their quest to defeat the evil Lord Monotone and prevent him from using the coveted Mirror Moon to force the galaxy into dancing along to his, and only his, tune. In this self-inflicted bullet hell you must stay on your toes as each laser beam fired ricochets off walls and can hit you too! Traverse randomly generated levels and face off Monotone’s various robotic machinations. Be it flamboyant flame sneakers or a cool rapid fire chrome suit - you decide how your favourite disco defender looks and plays based on what outfit you choose to wear. Time to save the galaxy and look like a cool cat!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/3136189a3357b9163eb6bdc23406750a.poster.avif?t=1726150836\" width=142 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/3136189a3357b9163eb6bdc23406750a.webm?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/3136189a3357b9163eb6bdc23406750a.mp4?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/e8710241ff4a908daae5556d56057b15.poster.avif?t=1726150836\" width=142 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/e8710241ff4a908daae5556d56057b15.webm?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/e8710241ff4a908daae5556d56057b15.mp4?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/dfd6ead49efa08343f15a1498c923a76.poster.avif?t=1726150836\" width=142 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/dfd6ead49efa08343f15a1498c923a76.webm?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/dfd6ead49efa08343f15a1498c923a76.mp4?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/a97c1afb865dde871c33f8338b6beed1.poster.avif?t=1726150836\" width=142 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/a97c1afb865dde871c33f8338b6beed1.webm?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452920/extras/a97c1afb865dde871c33f8338b6beed1.mp4?t=1726150836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>•\tThanks to randomly generated levels no play through is the same<br>•\tChoose your own look and play style with different characters and outfit combinations<br>•\tOnline leader boards shows you the “master of the dance floor”<br>•\tIncredibly groovy 70’s disco style soundtrack<br>•\tFunky visuals inspired by 70s fashion and cheesy sci-fi flicks",
